**Properties** are used to build custom forms and gather input from the user.

## Types of Properties

* [User-Defined Properties](/developer-guide/properties/user-defined): Properties you can create on demand.

platformOS also provides a few Properties for you to use:

* [Arrays](/developer-guide/properties/arrays): used to store multiple values for the same property.

* [Custom Images](/developer-guide/properties/custom-images): used to add one or many images to the configuration.

* [Custom Attachments](/developer-guide/properties/custom-attachments): used to add one or many files to the configuration.
